text.section:
A criminal solicitation is a:
Class C felony when the crime solicited is a violation of KRS 521.020 or 521.050;
Class B felony when the crime solicited is a Class A felony or capital offense;
Class C felony when the crime solicited is a Class B felony;
Class A misdemeanor when the crime solicited is a Class C or D felony;
Class B misdemeanor when the crime solicited is a misdemeanor.
